data.meta_description: Albanian_banknotes_historical_symbols_6129_2_7195 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides background information on the national currency of Albania. It discusses the history of Albania's central bank beginning in 1925. It describes the original currency, the golden frang, and subsequent changes including replacing the frang with the lek in 1947. The current banknote series features prominent historical figures from different periods of Albania's history.
